Allowed Armor Types

If you need a different type or higher AC, clear it with a god first.

TYPE    MAX CLASS     DESCRIPTION
armor       5         -- covers torso
helmet      2         -- covers head and neck
shield      2         -- covers shield side and front of body
ring        2         -- magic ring
amulet      2         -- magic amulet
boot        2         -- covers feet
glove       2         -- covers hands
cloak       2         -- magic or non-magical covers upper body
